The paper deals with video processing and analysis using deep learning techniques, which is a core topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes techniques for query processing on video streams, which involves database management (cs.DB) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) principles. The paper also utilizes statistical techniques for aggregate queries, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM) and machine learning (cs.LG) categories.
